column2: # This is a minimal framework for training xgboost in R using caret to do the cross-validation/grid tuning and using the normalized gini metric for scoring. The
# of CV folds and size of the tuning grid are limited to remain under kaggle kernel limits.
# To improve the score up the nrounds and expand the tuning grid.
